oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Trace Mineral Deficiencies (Cu, Se, Mg) Causing Reproductive Losses in a Purebred Angus Beef Herd
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Schneider, C. S.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: herd health
trace mineral deficiencies
reproduction
neonatal calf performance
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Reported here are results of a herd investigation that was undertaken to resolve chronic poor herd reproductive and neonatal calf performance in a sixty head purebred Angus beef herd.
